The paper discusses a strategy for learning neural network modules that can be combined in different ways to improve performance in robotics-related problems. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
